[src:1888-baltimore-orioles-season/1882-baltimore-orioles-season] The 19th century's version of the **Baltimore Orioles** were founded in 1882 as part of the new American Association.
[src:1888-baltimore-orioles-season/1882-baltimore-orioles-season] Owned by wealthy Harry Von der Horst, the Orioles finished the season in last place with only 19 wins.
[src:1888-baltimore-orioles-season/1888-boston-beaneaters-season] The **1888 Boston Beaneaters season** was the 18th season of the franchise.
